honors.description:
I received a "Achievement Award" for working on projects like SCS/E letters and E chat. Strategic Consumer Solution/E letters was the major project for retail consumer finance portfolio for GE, that involved validating the letters on the First data query tool which are sent to the customers for their queries and also integrating E-service with the First data query tool, so that whenever the customer visits the website for there query the letter would automatically be generated to the customer as per the requirement.

E chat being the pilot project, I was nominated to lead the project from the user acceptance testing point, this project involved communicating with the trainers in Manila, project managers, IT teams, Middleware teams, Business Analysts on daily basis and gathering the business requirements, creating and testing the test scripts for the entire application, cross training the team, reporting the issues, sending daily reports.
Was also nominated by the project manager to be a spokesperson for this project, on a Global All Hands call with the CEO of GE "Margaret Kean".
